AWS Certificate Reporting

This app is comprised of three components:


(1) A scripted input that pulls the list of certificates setup in AWS IAM  (defined in inputs.conf)
(2) A set of parsing rules that takes the JSON output of the scripted input and splits each certificate into a Splunk event (props.conf)
(3) A dashboard that reports on the certificates, highlights ones expiring soon and provides filtering options

for more information, www https://idelta.co.uk



